A consultant is a person who takes the watch off your hand and tells you the time.
A psychologist is a person who looks at everyone else when a beautiful girl walks into a room.
A professor is a person who has the skill to talk to other people when they are asleep.
The teacher is a woman who once thought she loved children.
A programmer is a person who solves a problem that you didn't know about in a way that you don't understand.
A lawyer is a person who is able to write a 10-page document and call it short.
